News for the European Commission about Horizon 2020 and Mathematics:
&ldquo;The online consultation on mathematics was carried out from 29 January to 15 May 2016 by the European Commission Directorate General for Communications Networks, Content &amp; Technology (DG CONNECT) in the context of a stakeholder consultation to prepare the Horizon 2020 Work Programme 2018-2020.&rdquo;
